  Type 'undefined' is not assignable to type 'Foo'. [plugin angular-compiler]

    src/main.ts:33:13:
      33 │           {{ foo | assertFoo }}
         ╵              ~~~


✘ [ERROR] NG2: Object is possibly 'undefined'. [plugin angular-compiler]

    src/main.ts:34:17:
      34 │           {{ foo.bar | assertNumber }}
         ╵                  ~~~


✘ [ERROR] NG5: Argument of type 'number | undefined' is not assignable to parameter of type 'number'.
  Type 'undefined' is not assignable to type 'number'. [plugin angular-compiler]

    src/main.ts:34:17:
